{"tid":1720772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[講三次] 朝早先係大春袋 朝早先係大春袋 朝早先係大春袋","createTime":"2019-11-14T12:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T01:15:50.000Z","uid":104425,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6e9cc6e59b9b7b5b6e2f255368c91e26ec4723bd","tid":1720772,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:56:18.000Z","msg":"黎明行動其實好成功<br />\n成功驗證咗朝早係春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以狗先想將戰場拉返去大學入面<br />\n再不時放風/佯攻<br />\n盡量拖散黎明行動/快閃<br />\n同埋製造留守vs離開嘅內訌<br />\n對於大學戰線點打<br />\n我有以下諗法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 盡快清理敏感物品</span></span><br />\n講緊嘅係個人/學生會電腦，其他例如關於魔法，甚至文宣等一切同運動/政治有關嘅文件，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">帶返屋企或者安全地方。</span> 因為呢啲係我哋嘅真春袋，強行攻入拎到就GG.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 心理戰</span></span><br />\n你話佢毅進狗，但指揮果班假假地都有degree架。而家攻一攻，刺激我地保校心理，變相令我地覺得campus=春袋。為保campus呢個「春袋」，減弱咗對黎明春袋嘅攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n而家個兩難係：你退佢就隨時攻，你守喺入面又浪費人力，狗隻可以以逸代勞。佢只要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">製造uncertainty</span>，我地係好被動。<br />\n<br />\n咁我地點解唔學敵人果招，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">製造uncertainty</span>? 之前咪有巴打講過，大學chem lab有好多料。只要有一定數量勇武留守，再喺連登，tg鳩噏下，我地一樣可以令狗狗有所顧忌。呢樣要召喚化學高手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 攻入咗又如何？</span></span><br />\n呢點就要連返去第1點嘅春袋論。冇晒敏感嘢後，其實campus只係個偽春袋。至於HKIX果啲，我就唔信嘅，大家都可以睇返相關理據。<br />\n<br />\n況且，比佢攻入咗搞爛個campus, 咁咪再罷課罷耐啲，又中咗我地個圈套。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加上個做法同紅衛兵一樣，又再多個文宣籌碼。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 攻咗入去，我地就輸？</span></span><br />\n大家都會想守護到campus, 我當然明。但要明白，強如武裝曱甴，全職打仗，一樣會有漏洞：立法會，支聯辦，狗屋，狗舍，狗車，無數封鎖消息嘅麻包袋。就算俾佢地搞冧campus, 我地一樣會贏盡國際戰線。相反，佢地嘅春袋被搞，只會換嚟全港恥笑（除咗沉默未過數果堆）。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 比狗浪費咗人力守campus, 好唔抵！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n解決方法：留守campus嘅人，專責campus附近嘅rb. 你要我地留人喺度，想冇代價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，呼籲大家聽日準時<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">揸春袋</span></span>，多你一個好多！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4bt0hK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4bt0hK.jpg&h=20b62b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要攬炒！</span></span>"},{"pid":"7e9452a1ba284a3116a442add0225d4e6721b81c","tid":1720772,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:59:03.000Z","msg":"1115 一日行動"},{"pid":"47b85a508fdc044eae9404bf1dae85dcff35c1ee","tid":1720772,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:59:32.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3918be772ed896fb6f7bf5e15764b6706c3fead4","tid":1720772,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"1115 一日行動"},{"pid":"e912af729cf9fd05e97755f5acfd3d9f5cef59d8","tid":1720772,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:00:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c9adead9619b3d80efd0880f3da108c70428da8","tid":1720772,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:01:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24cc1a5152f55dcab8dba087f16371b3969fc212","tid":1720772,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3tywbMy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3tywbMy.jpg&h=df6e8516&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed263c6cd6fde3cdb08fe39e6528a3b7887cc727","tid":1720772,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:01:40.000Z","msg":"1115 旭日行動"},{"pid":"3803f2abf3bbbc47b4b26017b469fa84081e7e10","tid":1720772,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:03:01.000Z","msg":"1115 旭日行動"},{"pid":"a511868882cc5eb8a430d0ecc0e8251aa810a77a","tid":1720772,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:03:02.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n但不棄守campus"},{"pid":"2e0e6c80e7cb1cef7749a3d378b88daa574050ca","tid":1720772,"uid":104425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a511868882cc5eb8a430d0ecc0e8251aa810a77a","tid":1720772,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:03:02.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n但不棄守campus"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:04:35.000Z","msg":"非棄守<br />\n但覺得priority唔係第一<br />\n<br />\n況且cu部份退守可以用山埃tg嘅健康理由<br />\n冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edb41fd03d96f98c02734b96d6906250bbf6ab3","tid":1720772,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:05:41.000Z","msg":"久守必失 留有退路"},{"pid":"8b16f79612f7e4a7336de9f55d66e999bb8e41c5","tid":1720772,"uid":131326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:06:30.000Z","msg":"黑警毅進狗死全家，落地獄，每日被過百萬市民詛咒你地絕對無好下場，信不信由你，我地唔會殺狗，唔會接狗仔狗女放學，狗閪警，你地可以24小時睇實家人與及狗仔女嗎？<br />\n<br />\n黑警毅進狗我屌你老母，吹撚脹?"},{"pid":"9aa3101ae2bab5b94bd758f170c8a337165c1055","tid":1720772,"uid":8680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"罷工2日 被罷一日嘅我可以同你地講 黎明行動真係好成功！ 公司無得話你 你不停影相 返唔到"},{"pid":"acf894dc805cc6ac3e87038f431f1c5b9a48992c","tid":1720772,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:23:04.000Z","msg":"1115 旭日行動"},{"pid":"7d5a531d508a423ead83ed3fd26959562c56a1d6","tid":1720772,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:38:52.000Z","msg":"1115 旭日行動"},{"pid":"3f